      "span_text": "To induce fat overloading of cells, human hepatocytes and HepG2 cells at 80% confluency were cultured for 24 h in complete medium containing 1 mM long-chain mixed FFAs (oleate acid and palmitate (SigmaAldrich) mixed at a final ratio of 2:1 and bound to 1% defatted BSA (Equitech-Bio) [CITATION_1] ."
